
as a client I want to set the desired parameters and for the system to remember them so that I do not set them every time and save my time

As a client i want to have an account where i can always login so my data is saved and i would not have to type in my data every time

As a client, I want to set the desired parameters and for the system to find me a sample for them, so that I can buy the desired watch

as a client, I want the system to find the watch itself and send me a message so that I can buy the desired watch faster

